{"tid":902414,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：經濟系學生最濫交　大學有4.88個性伴","createTime":"2018-11-14T19:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T02:42:19.000Z","uid":197852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"861387a83ba0e11b92e511aaee47e0b8e1ccdb0e","tid":902414,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:49:47.000Z","msg":"含大又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9a1b1851d8631f65d4ab36f3fcf0fb43603b34","tid":902414,"uid":197852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20120928/144552/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=twad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR20T3PhVOxfhUBGjjBYrrZiu3Fm71-RgdTHYnsJC8GDL7ExfZxMEvwrMAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20120928%2F144552%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR20T3PhVOxfhUBGjjBYrrZiu3Fm71-RgdTHYnsJC8GDL7ExfZxMEvwrMAM&d=sIGfopfUIAdzml7A%2BFiBPv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=85f96127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20120928%2F144552%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR20T3PhVOxfhUBGjjBYrrZiu3Fm71-RgdTHYnsJC8GDL7ExfZxMEvwrMAM&h=26006f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20120928/144552/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=twad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR20T3PhVOxfhUBGjjBYrrZiu3Fm71-RgdTHYnsJC8GDL7ExfZxMEvwrMAM</a>"},{"pid":"394fb1326a4f4cf79612d286949e1a738de04778","tid":902414,"uid":197852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:50:45.000Z","msg":"這是一份最新的英國調查報告，由《<a href=\"http://StudentBeans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FStudentBeans.com&d=sIGfopfUIAdzml7A%2BFiBPv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d3c7bcf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">StudentBeans.com</a>》網站所完成，共訪問了4656名大學生。<br />\n在一般人的傳統印象中，大學讀經濟系的學生，應該都是比較保守、勤奮與認真的，但在這次的調查中卻發現，原來經濟系學生才是大學校園內最「濫交」的一群，平均每個人在大學生涯中有4.88個性伴侶。<br />\n其次是就讀社工系的學生，有4.7個性伴侶，之後是行銷學系的學生，有4.57個性伴侶；第四是旅遊系學生，有4.56個性伴侶，排行第五是農業科系學生，平均有4.55個性伴侶。<br />\n那排行最差的呢？<br />\n墊底的是環境科學系的學生，大學期間，平均只有1.71個性伴侶；好一點點的是神學系學生，平均有2.13個性伴侶；再來是地球科學系、教育學系和哲學系。<br />\n英國百所大學接受調查的這4656名大學生中，超過60%的大學生，在大學期間有超過2名以上的性伴侶，兒也有5%的大學生，大學期間沒有性伴侶。但，在這個調查中，高達52%的大學生們認為，大學期間，唸書比做愛重要。"},{"pid":"e30ddecee9b1973c136ce3f87bbbd0d358940a13","tid":902414,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"0個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dbe6109df5bad1be1358430d47ffd82cce3340","tid":902414,"uid":96146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:52:23.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a4154d83c477e45e3dfede10f689f51ad046a5","tid":902414,"uid":54930,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e30ddecee9b1973c136ce3f87bbbd0d358940a13","tid":902414,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"0個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:54:39.000Z","msg":"p&lt;0.05<br />\nReject null hypothesis <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf68ae1e026d7b8ebe9ea536b763d19af5bc9be","tid":902414,"uid":38416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:56:48.000Z","msg":"香港恒大起碼十幾個性伴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921ee6f409567bf166b148372b86c95a1f7e9169","tid":902414,"uid":3549,"